@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Processing : receive video suggestion request
Processing --> IdentifiedUser : identify user
IdentifiedUser --> GatheringVideos : gather videos based on profile and preferences
GatheringVideos --> TrendingVideos : include trending videos from user's area
TrendingVideos --> SimilarTags : include videos with similar tags
SimilarTags --> SameGenres : include videos from same genres
SameGenres --> PromotedVideos : include promoted videos
PromotedVideos --> AddingDetails : add details such as thumbnails and view counts
AddingDetails --> SendingSuggestions : send suggested videos to user
SendingSuggestions --> [*]
@enduml
